<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You Goodwall</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe, #00f2fe);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #0077ff;
            font-size: 42px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #00aaff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .heart {
            font-size: 40px;
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>Thank You, Goodwall!</h1>
        <p>
            I am truly grateful to <span class="highlight">Goodwall</span> for this amazing opportunity.
        </p>
        <p>
            Through this journey, I learned new skills, gained valuable experiences, 
            and discovered how powerful growth can be when opportunities meet dedication.
        </p>
        <p>
            Thank you for inspiring me to learn, improve, and believe in my potential.
        </p>
        <div class="heart">💙</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
